Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A Jedi Knight referred the young Human Zayne Carrick to the Jedi Enclave on the planet Dantooine in 3977 BBY. The Jedi Knight said that Carrick had "marginal" aptitude for the Force, an assertion supported by Jedi Master Vandar Tokare.

The Jedi Knight was briefly mentioned in a flashback on the first page of the second issue of the Knights of the Old Republic comic series, written by John Jackson Miller and released on February 22, 2006.
